&#xd;
</faultstring><detail><ns0:BusinessServiceException xmlns:ns0="http://oracle.e1.bssv.JP420000/">&#xd;

               requires the Customer Order Number to be entered.&#xd;
Resolution . . Enter a Customer Order Number.&#xd;
&#xd;
</faultstring><detail><ns0:BusinessServiceException xmlns:ns0="http://oracle.e1.bssv.JP420000/">&#xd;
B4204200 ProcessSOHeader::Cause. . . . . The Customer Master file (F0301) for the Sold-to Address Number&#xd;
               requires the Customer Order Number to be entered.&#xd;

&#xd;
</ns0:BusinessServiceException></detail></ns0:Fault></S:Body></S:Envelope>
